### ============================================
### 商品列表（支援分頁和篩選）
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?limit=3
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
### 排序asc
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?order=asc
### 排序desc
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?order=desc
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
### 篩選: 商品分類, 排序: 時間desc
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?category=electronics&orderBy=createdAt&order=desc
### 篩選: 商品分類, 排序: 時間asc
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?category=electronics&orderBy=createdAt&order=asc
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
### 篩選: 價格範圍, 排序: 時間desc
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?minPrice=10&maxPrice=9999&orderBy=price&order=desc
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
### 篩選: 價格範圍, 排序: 時間asc
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?minPrice=10&maxPrice=9999&orderBy=price&order=asc
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
### 篩選: 價格範圍, 排序: 價格asc
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?minPrice=10&maxPrice=9999&orderBy=price&order=asc
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
### 商品列表: 測試
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?minPrice=11&maxPrice=9999&orderBy=price&order=asc
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

